'''Rivers''' has been introduced in OpenTTD during the development towards [[en/Archive/OpenTTD/OpenTTD 0.6.0]] (more concret in r11926). The first testing-release which contained the feature was OpenTTD 0.6.0-beta 4. Rivers are similar to [[en/Manual/Water Transport Tiles]] but can be generated during the map generation-process(since r22767).